      "As a quadruple certified contractor (GAF Master Elite, CertainTeed Platinum Preferred, Malarkey, and Emerald Premium), Gates Enterprises can install any of these products with the highest available manufacturer warranty [LINK: certifications]. That flexibility allows us to recommend the best product for your specific situation rather than pushing whatever brand we happen to carry.",
      "Do Class 4 Shingles Really Hold Up in Colorado Storms?",
